keyFacts: This document tracks housing assignments for Federal Bureau of Prisons inmate with register number 86824-054.
The inmate was frequently moved between different housing units, ranges, and beds, indicating possible administrative segregation, protective custody, or routine prison management.
The record spans from April 2019 to July 2021, showing continuous incarceration during this period.
